@startuml Sequence_Payment

actor Customer
participant "Client" as Client
participant "Payment API" as API
participant "Database" as DB
participant "VNPay" as VNPay

== Checkout ==
Customer -> Client: View cart
Customer -> Client: Click checkout
Client -> API: POST /api/payments/create
API -> DB: Get cart items
DB --> API: Cart data
API -> API: Calculate total
API -> DB: Create order
DB --> API: Order created
API -> VNPay: Create payment request
VNPay --> API: Payment URL/QR
API --> Client: Return payment info
Client --> Customer: Display payment URL/QR

== Payment Processing ==
Customer -> VNPay: Complete payment
VNPay -> VNPay: Process payment
VNPay -> API: Payment callback (webhook)
API -> API: Verify payment
API -> DB: Update order status
DB --> API: Order updated
API -> DB: Grant product access
DB --> API: Access granted
API -> Customer: Send confirmation email
VNPay --> Customer: Payment success page

== Payment Verification ==
Customer -> Client: Return from VNPay
Client -> API: GET /api/payments/verify
API -> VNPay: Verify payment status
VNPay --> API: Payment status
API -> DB: Update order if needed
DB --> API: Order status
API --> Client: Payment result
Client --> Customer: Show confirmation

@enduml

